676
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,470
No, that was just a joke.

677
00:26:34,690 --> 00:26:35,920
By the way,

678
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,920
could you sometime

679
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,450
