00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:48,760
We need shirts totaling $100,000.

793
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:50,130
Can you handle that?

794
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:54,000
No problem.

795
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,030
Absolutely no problem.

